#: ../../source/joint.rst:4
msgid "Joint (Constraints)"
msgstr "关节（约束）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:7
msgid "Add Joint"
msgstr "添加关节"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:10
msgid "Add Joint Between Two Rigid Bodies"
msgstr "在两个刚体之间添加关节"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:11
msgid "Switch to *Object Mode*."
msgstr "切换到 *对象模式*。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:12
msgid "Select the two rigid bodies to which you want to add a constraint."
msgstr "选择需要添加约束的两个刚体。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:13 ../../source/joint.rst:49
msgid "Click the :menuselection:`+` button."
msgstr "点击 :menuselection:`+` 按钮。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:14 ../../source/joint.rst:50
msgid "Configure the joint properties, then press :menuselection:`OK` to comfirm."
msgstr "配置关节属性，然后点击 :menuselection:`OK` 确认。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:22
msgid ""
"You can find detailed explanations of all joint parameters in :ref:`Joint"
" Properties <joint_properties>`."
msgstr "有关所有关节参数的详细说明，请参阅 :ref:`关节属性 <joint_properties>`。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:23
msgid "``Use Bone Rotation``:"
msgstr "``Use Bone Rotation``："

#: ../../source/joint.rst:25
msgid ""
"When enabled, the joint's orientation will be aligned with the "
"orientation of the associated bone."
msgstr "启用后，关节的方向将与关联骨骼的方向保持一致。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:27
msgid ""
"Disabling this option keeps the default joint orientation instead of "
"matching the bone."
msgstr "禁用该选项时，关节将保持默认方向，而不会与骨骼方向对齐。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:29
msgid "``Is Lateral Joint``:"
msgstr "``Is Lateral Joint``："

#: ../../source/joint.rst:31
msgid ""
"Indicates that the joint connects two rigid bodies belonging to different"
" bone chains (for example, neighboring skirt chains)."
msgstr "表示该关节连接的是来自不同骨骼链的两个刚体（例如相邻的裙子骨骼链）。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:33
msgid ""
"When this option is enabled, the add-on places the joint at the midpoint "
"between the two rigid bodies and computes an averaged orientation to "
"produce a stable constraint."
msgstr "启用该选项后，插件会将关节放置在两个刚体之间的中点位置，并计算平均方向，以生成一个稳定的约束。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:36
msgid ""
"While it is technically possible to create multiple joints between the "
"same pair of rigid bodies, do so with caution."
msgstr "虽然在技术上可以在同一对刚体之间创建多个关节，但请谨慎使用。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:38
msgid ""
"If you accidentally create duplicates when only one joint is needed, the "
"simulation may behave unexpectedly."
msgstr "如果你只需要一个关节，但却误创了多个重复关节，模拟结果可能会出现异常。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:40
msgid ""
"You can verify duplicates in the :ref:`Joint List <joint_list>` and "
"`Outliner`"
msgstr "你可以在 :ref:`关节列表 <joint_list>` 或 `大纲视图（Outliner）` 中检查是否存在重复关节。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:46
msgid "Add Joints Along a Bone Chain"
msgstr "沿骨骼链添加关节"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:47
msgid "Switch to *Object Mode*"
msgstr "切换到 *对象模式*。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:48
msgid ""
"Select all rigid bodies along the same bone chain that require "
"constraints."
msgstr "选择同一骨骼链上所有需要添加约束的刚体。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:58
msgid ""
"When both bone-chain rigid bodies (e.g. A, B, C) and unrelated rigid "
"bodies (e.g. D, E) are selected, the add-on will only create joints "
"between the bone-chain rigid bodies (A, B, C). The others (D, E) will be "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"当同时选择骨骼链上的刚体（例如 A、B、C）以及不相关的刚体（例如 "
"D、E）时，插件只会在骨骼链刚体（A、B、C）之间创建关节，其余对象（D、E）会被忽略。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:63
msgid ""
"Rigid bodies from different bone chains must be connected one pair at a "
"time — batch operations are **Not** supported in this case."
msgstr "来自不同骨骼链的刚体必须逐对连接，**不支持批量操作**。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:66
msgid ""
"For example, when adding joints between rigid bodies from different skirt"
" bone chains, they must be added individually."
msgstr "例如，在为裙子不同骨骼链之间的刚体添加关节时，需要逐个添加。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:68
msgid ""
"This limitation exists because each model has a different structure and "
"design. We prioritize flexibility and compatibility over full automation."
msgstr "之所以存在这一限制，是因为每个模型的结构和设计都不相同。相比完全自动化，我们更优先保证系统的灵活性和兼容性。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:74
msgid "Save Presets"
msgstr "保存预设"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:75
msgid "See also: :ref:`Rigid Body Save Presets <save_presets>`"
msgstr "另请参阅：:ref:`刚体保存预设 <save_presets>`"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:80
msgid "Joint Properties"
msgstr "关节属性"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:82
msgid "**Name**: The name of the joint."
msgstr "**Name**：关节名称"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:84
msgid "**Limit X Upper**: Upper limit of linear motion along the **X** axis."
msgstr "**Limit X Upper**：沿 **X** 轴线性运动的上限"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:85
msgid "**Limit Y Upper**: Upper limit of linear motion along the **Y** axis."
msgstr "**Limit Y Upper**：沿 **Y** 轴线性运动的上限"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:86
msgid "**Limit Z Upper**: Upper limit of linear motion along the **Z** axis."
msgstr "**Limit Z Upper**：沿 **Z** 轴线性运动的上限"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:87
msgid "**Limit X Lower**: Lower limit of linear motion along the **X** axis."
msgstr "**Limit X Lower**：沿 **X** 轴线性运动的下限"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:88
msgid "**Limit Y Lower**: Lower limit of linear motion along the **Y** axis."
msgstr "**Limit Y Lower**：沿 **Y** 轴线性运动的下限"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:89
msgid "**Limit Z Lower**: Lower limit of linear motion along the **Z** axis."
msgstr "**Limit Z Lower**：沿 **Z** 轴线性运动的下限"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:91
msgid ""
"**Limit Ang X Upper**: Upper angular limit around the **X** axis (*in "
"degrees*)."
msgstr "**Limit Ang X Upper**：绕 **X** 轴的旋转上限（*单位：度*）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:92
msgid ""
"**Limit Ang Y Upper**: Upper angular limit around the **Y** axis (*in "
"degrees*)."
msgstr "**Limit Ang Y Upper**：绕 **Y** 轴的旋转上限（*单位：度*）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:93
msgid ""
"**Limit Ang Z Upper**: Upper angular limit around the **Z** axis (*in "
"degrees*)."
msgstr "**Limit Ang Z Upper**：绕 **Z** 轴的旋转上限（*单位：度*）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:94
msgid ""
"**Limit Ang X Lower**: Lower angular limit around the **X** axis (*in "
"degrees*)."
msgstr "**Limit Ang X Lower**：绕 **X** 轴的旋转下限（*单位：度*）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:95
msgid ""
"**Limit Ang Y Lower**: Lower angular limit around the **Y** axis (*in "
"degrees*)."
msgstr "**Limit Ang Y Lower**：绕 **Y** 轴的旋转下限（*单位：度*）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:96
msgid ""
"**Limit Ang Z Lower**: Lower angular limit around the **Z** axis (*in "
"degrees*)."
msgstr "**Limit Ang Z Lower**：绕 **Z** 轴的旋转下限（*单位：度*）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:98
msgid ""
"**Spring Linear**: The spring stiffness that controls linear motion "
"(Higher values produce stronger resistance when the joint is displaced)."
msgstr "**Spring Linear**：控制线性运动的弹簧刚度（值越大，关节位移时阻力越强）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:99
msgid ""
"**Spring Angular**: The spring stiffness that controls angular motion "
"(Higher values produce stronger torque resistance when the joint is "
"rotated)."
msgstr "**Spring Angular**：控制角向运动的弹簧刚度（值越大，关节旋转时扭矩阻力越强）"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:102
msgid ""
"The parameters above correspond to Blender's built-in *Rigid Body "
"Constraint* properties."
msgstr "上述参数对应 Blender 内置的 *刚体约束* 属性。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:107
msgid "Joint Properties Panel"
msgstr "关节属性面板"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:109
msgid ""
"The *Joint Properties Panel* is where you can view and edit all joint-"
"related attributes."
msgstr "*关节属性面板* 用于查看和编辑所有关节相关属性。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:111
msgid "It can be found under the *Physics Tab* in Blender."
msgstr "可以在 Blender 的 *物理选项卡（Physics Tab）* 下找到。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:121
msgid "Joint List"
msgstr "关节列表"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:123
msgid ""
"The *Joint List* displays all joints (*Rigid Body Constraint*) in the "
"current scene."
msgstr "*关节列表* 显示当前场景中所有的关节（ *刚体约束* ）。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:125
msgid ""
"By default, it filters by :menuselection:`Active Model`, displaying only "
"the joints of the currently selected model."
msgstr "默认情况下，按 :menuselection:`Active Model` 过滤，仅显示当前选中模型的关节。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:127
msgid ""
"To view joints from all models, change the filter to :menuselection:`All "
"Models`."
msgstr "要查看所有模型的关节，请将过滤器更改为 :menuselection:`All Models`。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:135
msgid "Reordering List Items"
msgstr "列表项排序"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:136
msgid ""
"You can reorder list items using the :menuselection:`⬆` and "
":menuselection:`⬇` buttons, or through the right-side dropdown menu "
"options: :menuselection:`Move To Top` and :menuselection:`Move To "
"Bottom`."
msgstr ""
"可以使用 :menuselection:`⬆` 和 :menuselection:`⬇` 按钮重新排序列表项，或通过右侧下拉菜单选项 "
":menuselection:`Move To Top` 和 :menuselection:`Move To Bottom` 进行排序。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:145
msgid "Error Indicators"
msgstr "错误提示"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:148
msgid "Missing Joint"
msgstr "关节缺失"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:149
msgid ""
"A *\"Missing Joint\"* icon appears when the list entry has no valid "
"*Rigid Body Constraint* data."
msgstr "当列表项没有有效的 *刚体约束（Rigid Body Constraint）* 数据时，会显示 *“关节缺失”* 图标。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:151
msgid ""
"This usually occurs when the joint was deleted from Blender's constraint "
"system but still exists in the add-on's list."
msgstr "这种情况通常发生在关节已从 Blender 的约束系统中删除，但仍存在于插件列表中。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:153
msgid ""
"To fix this, recreate the joint using the :menuselection:`Add Rigid Body "
"Constraint` button in the :ref:`Joint Properties Panel "
"<joint_properties_panel>`."
msgstr ""
"要修复此问题，请在 :ref:`关节属性面板 <joint_properties_panel>` 中使用 :menuselection:`Add "
"Rigid Body Constraint` 按钮重新创建关节。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:161
msgid "Missing Linked Objects"
msgstr "关联对象缺失"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:162
msgid ""
"A *\"Missing Linked Objects\"* icon appears when one or both of the rigid"
" bodies linked by the joint are missing."
msgstr "当关节关联的一个或两个刚体缺失时，会显示 *“关联对象缺失”* 图标。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:164
msgid ""
"For example, if ``Object1`` or ``Object2`` is not assigned, the joint "
"cannot function properly."
msgstr "例如，如果 ``Object1`` 或 ``Object2`` 未被分配，关节将无法正常工作。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:166
msgid ""
"You can reassign the missing objects in the :ref:`Joint Properties Panel "
"<joint_properties_panel>`."
msgstr "可以在 :ref:`关节属性面板 <joint_properties_panel>` 中重新分配缺失对象。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:174
msgid ""
"It is generally recommended to assign the **static** or **bone-driven** "
"rigid body as ``Object1``, and the **simulated** rigid body as "
"``Object2``."
msgstr "通常建议将 **静态** 或 **骨骼驱动** 刚体设置为 ``Object1``，将 **模拟** 刚体设置为 ``Object2``。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:176
msgid ""
"This setup ensures a more stable and predictable constraint behavior, "
"because Blender internally treats ``Object1`` as the reference frame for "
"the joint's position and rotation limits."
msgstr "这种设置可确保约束行为更稳定且可预测，因为 Blender 内部将 ``Object1`` 视为关节位置和旋转限制的参考框架。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:179
msgid "Invalid Joint Pair"
msgstr "无效的关节对"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:180
msgid ""
"An *\"Invalid Joint Pair\"* icon appears when both linked objects "
"(``Object1`` and ``Object2``) refer to the same rigid body object."
msgstr "当两个关联对象（``Object1`` 和 ``Object2``）指向同一个刚体对象时，会显示 *“无效关节对”* 图标。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:182
msgid "This setup is invalid because a joint requires two distinct rigid bodies."
msgstr "此设置无效，因为一个关节需要两个不同的刚体。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:184
msgid "Recreate the joint with two different rigid bodies to resolve this issue."
msgstr "请使用两个不同的 *刚体* 重新创建 *关节* 以解决此问题。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:192
msgid "Remove Joint"
msgstr "移除关节"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:194
msgid "Select a joint in the *3D viewport*, the *Joint List*, or the *Outliner*"
msgstr "在 *3D视图*、*关节列表* 或 *大纲视图（Outliner）* 中选择一个关节"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:195
msgid "Click the :menuselection:`-` button to remove it."
msgstr "点击 :menuselection:`-` 按钮将其移除。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:197
msgid "See also: :ref:`Remove Rigid Body <remove_rigid_body>`."
msgstr "另请参阅：:ref:`移除刚体 <remove_rigid_body>`。"

